                     <interp inst="t18330214-151-off848" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18330214-151-cd849" type="crimeDate">13th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18330214-151-off848 t18330214-151-cd849"></join>, at St. George, Hanover-square, 2 sovereigns and one 50l. Bank note, the monies of 
                     
